  "remarks": "Re-appointed in September 2019 as Member of the Federal Council of Russia representing the State Council of Crimea for a second five-year term (until 2024).  Former Vice Speaker of the Crimean Parliament.  Initiated, together with Sergey Aksyonov, the unlawful dismissal of the government of the Autonomous Republic of Crimea.  One of the first Crimean Leaders to ask in public for the annexation of Crimea to Russia; Listing: Listed on 19 Jun. 2014 (re-listed on 16 Jun. 2017, 10 June 2020 and 10 June 2023)",
